spect du DIH</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/fr/guerre-et-droit/defis-contemporains-pour-le-dih/terrorisme" title="">Terrorisme et DIH</a></li><li class="last leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/fr/nos-activites/violences-sexuelles" title="">Violences sexuelles</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class="visible-sm visible-xs list-languages"> <select class="styled-language-select i-arrow-down-after redirection-select"><option value="https://www.icrc.org/fr" selected="selected">FR</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/en">EN</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/es">ES</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/pt">PT</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/zh">ZH</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/ar">AR</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/ru">RU</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/de">DE</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/it">IT</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/en/languages">Autre</option> </select></div></div></div></div> </header></div> <nav class="navbar navbar--main clearfix js_navbar" id="main-menu" role="navigation"><div class="container"><div class="nav-sub"> <button type="button" class="nav-toggle i-menu pull-left js_toggle" data-target=".navbar--main"> <span class="sr-only">Afficher la navigation</span> </button><div class="pull-right"><div class="nav-donate nav-link-main-container visible-sm visible-xs"> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/fr/don" class="bg-red nav-link-main">Faites un don</a></div><div class="nav-search nav-link-main-container with-social "> <a href="#" class="i-search nav-link-main js_toggle" data-target=".nav-search"> <span class="sr-only">Recherche</span> </a><form action="https://www.icrc.org/fr/resource-centre/result" method="get" class="nav-submenu"><div class="container"> <input type="search" name="t" value="" /> <button> <i class="i-search i-search--small visible-xs"></i> <span class="hidden-xs">Recherche</span> </button></div></form></div> <secti